<span style="font-weight: 400;">Antibiotic treatments for tonsillitis are easily available. Over-the-counter drugs are also available. Having said that, a mild tonsillitis will not require you to take on any more medicines while a severe case of the ailment may even require you to undergo a surgery (tonsillectomy).</span>

